          "content": "### MAJOR ANDERSON IS DOWN\n**TIME:** 12:00 PM EST, October 27\n\n**The Incident:**\nThe crisis has drawn its first blood. A U-2 spy plane, piloted by Major Rudolf Anderson, has disappeared from radar over Cuba. Debris confirms it was hit by a Soviet SA-2 Surface-to-Air Missile (SAM). Major Anderson is dead.\n\n**The Standing Order:**\nPreviously, the ExComm and the President had agreed on a clear 'tit-for-tat' policy: *If the Soviets shoot down a US plane, we will immediately bomb the SAM site that fired the missile.* The Air Force is already fueling jets in Florida. They are waiting for the 'Go' code to launch the retaliation strike. The Generals argue that failing to strike back now destroys US credibility and invites further attacks."
